	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Not much has been done on that front since the last time we talked about the wiki.  It just when I see the result of the PPU table that I just converted from nestech yesterday, it feels so icky compared the previous ascii art version. 
<br />
<br />The ascii art one was easier on the eye to read for the format.  Maybe there is some way to make nice tables in wiki format. It just that I don't know how and the syntax is quite cumbersome.  The same could be said about ascii art from the text area in a webpage (i.e. cannot easily put tab character etc).
<br />
<br />When you talk about meta-data, can you elaborate on the subject?  What kind of meta-data I could put in those table?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


